## Getting Started

```sh
# Pull an image
podman pull ghcr.io/daemonless/radarr:latest

# Run with PUID/PGID mapping
podman run -d --name radarr \
  -e PUID=1000 -e PGID=1000 \
  -v /data/radarr:/config \
  -v /media:/media \
  ghcr.io/daemonless/radarr:latest
```

